<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GIIS Robotics Club</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="resources/favicon.ico">
    <style>
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'crest';
            src: url('/crst.otf') format('opentype');
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'crestb';
            src: url('/crstb.otf') format('opentype');
        }
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        html, body{
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #111111;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-family: 'crest';
            background-image: url('/logo/background.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        
        *, *::before, *::after {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        /* anchor tags  --- logo ---- login url */
        ul{
            list-style-type: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        li{
            float: left;
        }
        a{
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 10px 9px;
            display: block;
            font-size: large;
        }
        nav{
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 15px clamp(20px, 5vw, 50px);
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(20, 33, 61, 0.8) 51%, rgba(30, 30, 47, 0.8) 100%);
            border-radius: 0 0 20px 20px;
            min-height: 72px;
            width: 100%;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        nav ul {
            display: flex;
            flex: 1;
            gap: 6px;
        }
        
        nav logo {
            position: absolute;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }
        
        nav > a {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: right;
        }
        
        
        .hamburger {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            background: rgba(20, 33, 61, 0.9);
            border: none;
            color: white;
            font-size: 24px;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            z-index: 1001;
        }

        .hamburger:hover {
            background: rgba(108, 99, 255, 0.8);
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .hamburger:active {
            transform: scale(0.95);
        }

        .mobile-nav {
            display: none;
            position: fixed;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(20, 33, 61, 0.96) 45%, rgba(30, 30, 47, 0.96) 100%);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            z-index: 1000;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .mobile-nav.active {
            display: flex;
        }

        .mobile-nav-inner {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 420px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 80px 32px 48px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        .mobile-nav-logo {
            width: clamp(140px, 45vw, 220px);
        }

        .mobile-nav-divider {
            width: 100%;
            height: 1px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            border: 0;
            border-radius: 999px;
        }

        .mobile-nav-label {
            align-self: flex-start;
            font-size: clamp(0.85rem, 2vw, 1rem);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: #bfbfbf;
            margin-top: 4px;
        }

        .mobile-nav-links {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 10px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .mobile-nav-link {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            background: linear-gradient(130deg, rgba(30,32,31,0.95) 56%, rgba(39,13,64,0.9) 100%) padding-box, linear-gradient(130deg, #7f7f7f, #282a29) border-box;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.6vw, 1.3rem);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            transition: transform 0.18s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease, background 0.25s ease;
        }

        .mobile-nav-link:hover,
        .mobile-nav-link:focus-visible {
            transform: translateX(4px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
            border-color: rgba(154,163,160,0.9);
            outline: none;
        }

        .mobile-nav-link:active {
            transform: translateX(1px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.28) inset;
        }

        .mobile-nav-link.active {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(82,108,218,1) 0%, rgba(44,75,205,1) 24%, rgba(82,108,218,1) 71%, rgba(82,108,218,1) 100%) padding-box, linear-gradient(to right, #2c4bcd, #2c4bcd) border-box;
            box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(66,84,214,0.35);
        }
        
        .main-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-image: url('/logo/optix.jpg');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            position: relative;
            padding: 100px 0 0;
        }
        
        .content-glass-container {
            margin: 40px clamp(20px, 5vw, 80px) 80px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(35,35,55,0.4), rgba(25,18,40,0.4));
            backdrop-filter: blur(25px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(25px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
            border-radius: 28px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.6), 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            min-height: calc(100vh - 200px);
        }
        
        .content-glass-container::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 85% 15%, rgba(108,99,255,0.08), transparent 60%);
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        
        .content-glass-container > * {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .hero-section {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 40px clamp(20px, 5vw, 50px) 60px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .hero-content {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 60px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            width: 100%;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .hero-text {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 24px;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        
        .hero-title {
            font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
            font-family: 'crestb';
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin: 0;
            color: #ffffff;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
        
        .hero-subtitle {
            font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem);
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        
        .hero-description {
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.2rem);
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            padding: 16px 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }
        
        .hero-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 16px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        
        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(82,108,218,1) 0%, rgba(44,75,205,1) 24%, rgba(82,108,218,1) 71%, rgba(82,108,218,1) 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-family: 'crest';
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 24px -6px rgba(66,84,214,0.35);
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }
        
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(98,122,230,1) 0%, rgba(54,85,215,1) 24%, rgba(98,122,230,1) 71%, rgba(98,122,230,1) 100%);
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 14px 30px -8px rgba(66,84,214,0.4);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            background: transparent;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-family: 'crest';
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }
        
        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .hero-card {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 32px 28px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(35,35,55,0.75), rgba(25,18,40,0.75));
            backdrop-filter: blur(25px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(25px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
            border-radius: 22px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.6), 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform .28s ease, box-shadow .28s ease;
        }
        
        .hero-card::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 85% 15%, rgba(108,99,255,0.15), transparent 60%);
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        
        .hero-card > * {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .hero-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            box-shadow: 0 35px 70px -15px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
        }
        

        
        ::-webkit-scrollbar {
            width: 12px;
        }
        
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
            background: rgba(10, 10, 29, 0.8);
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #1a1a3a;
        }
        
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c63ff, #4a47a3);
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(10, 10, 29, 0.8);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #5a52d5, #3e3b8a);
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(108, 99, 255, 0.4);
        }
        
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:active {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a42c0, #2e2b70);
        }
        
        ::-webkit-scrollbar-corner {
            background: rgba(10, 10, 29, 0.8);
        }
        
        html {
            scrollbar-width: thin;
            scrollbar-color: #6c63ff rgba(10, 10, 29, 0.8);
        }
        button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c63ff, #4a47a3);
            color: #ffffff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-family: 'crest';
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        footer{
            background-color: #171743;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 14px;
            border-top: 1px solid #444;
        }
        /* modern card style aligned with dashboard/login */
        .info{
            width: clamp(360px, 32vw, 480px);
            padding: 32px 28px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(35,35,55,0.75), rgba(25,18,40,0.75));
            backdrop-filter: blur(25px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(25px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
            border-radius: 22px;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.6), 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
            color: #fff;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: transform .28s ease, box-shadow .28s ease;
        }
        
        .info::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 85% 15%, rgba(108,99,255,0.15), transparent 60%);
            pointer-events: none;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        
        .info > * {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .info:hover {
            transform: translateY(-6px);
            box-shadow: 0 28px 60px -12px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
        }

        .info h2 {
            margin: 0 0 18px 0;
            font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.6vw, 2.2rem);
            line-height: 1.15;
            letter-spacing: 0.6px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .info .subtitle { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78); display:block; margin-bottom: 18px; }

        .btna {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 22px;
            font-family: 'crest';
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 0;
            cursor: pointer;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(82,108,218,1) 0%, rgba(44,75,205,1) 24% , rgba(82,108,218,1) 100%);
            color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 24px -6px rgba(66,84,214,0.25);
            transition: transform .18s ease, box-shadow .25s ease;
            text-transform: none;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .btna:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 14px 30px -10px rgba(66,84,214,0.35); }
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #e0e0ff;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: block;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hamburger {
                display: block;
            }
            
            nav ul {
                display: none;
            }
            
            nav > a {
                display: none;
            }
            
            .hero-content {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 40px;
                text-align: center;
            }
            

            
            .hero-actions {
                justify-content: center;
            }
            
            .btn-primary, .btn-secondary {
                padding: 12px 24px;
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .content-glass-container {
                margin: 20px 15px 40px;
                min-height: calc(100vh - 140px);
            }
            
            .hero-section {
                padding: 30px 20px 40px;
            }
            
            .features-section {
                padding: 50px 15px;
            }
            

            
            .hero-actions {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            
            .btn-primary, .btn-secondary {
                width: 100%;
                text-align: center;
                max-width: 280px;
            }
            
            footer {
                padding: 15px;
                font-size: 12px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="contact">Contact Us</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://blueprint.giisrobotics.club" target="_blank">Our Event</a></li>
        </ul>
        <logo>
            <a href="/" ><img src="/logo/logo-white.png" alt="GIIS Robotics Club Logo" width="60" height="60"></a>
        </logo>
    </nav>

    <div class="main-content">
        <div class="content-glass-container">
            <!-- Hero Section -->
            <section class="hero-section">
                <div class="hero-content">
                    <div class="hero-text">
                        <h1 class="hero-title">GIIS Robotics Club</h1>
                        <h2 class="hero-subtitle">Build. Break. Obsess. Repeat.</h2>
                        <p class="hero-description">
                            Where innovation meets engineering. Join Singapore's premier high school robotics community 
                            and transform your ideas into reality through cutting-edge technology and collaborative problem-solving.
                        </p>
                        <div class="hero-actions">
                            <a href="/about" class="btn-primary">Meet the Team</a>
                            <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary">Get Involved</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hero-card">
                        <div style="text-align: center; padding: 20px;">
                            <img src="/logo/logo-white.png" alt="GIIS Robotics Club Logo" width="120" height="120" style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                            <h3 style="margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 1.8rem; font-family: 'crestb';">Academic Year</h3>
                            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 2.2rem; color: #6c63ff; font-weight: 700;"><%= new Date().getMonth() >= 3 ? new Date().getFullYear() : new Date().getFullYear() - 1 %> - <%= new Date().getMonth() >= 3 ? new Date().getFullYear() + 1 : new Date().getFullYear() %></p>
                            <div style="margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);">
                                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);">
                                    Empowering the next generation of innovators through robotics, engineering, and technology.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div> 
    <footer>
        Developed by Vasipalli Eshan Aditya | Maintained by GIIS Robotics Club &copy; <%= new Date().getMonth() >= 3 ? new Date().getFullYear() : new Date().getFullYear() - 1 %> - <%= new Date().getMonth() >= 3 ? new Date().getFullYear() + 1 : new Date().getFullYear() %>
    </footer>
    
    <script>
        // Smooth scrolling for internal links
        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="#"]').forEach(anchor => {
            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                const targetId = this.getAttribute('href').substring(1);
                const targetElement = document.getElementById(targetId);
                if (targetElement) {
                    targetElement.scrollIntoView({
                        behavior: 'smooth',
                        block: 'start'
                    });
                }
            });
        });

        // Add loading animation when navigating to other pages
        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^="/"]').forEach(link => {
            link.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
                if (this.href !== window.location.href) {
                    this.style.opacity = '0.7';
                }
            });
        });

        // Parallax effect for hero section
        window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
            const scrolled = window.pageYOffset;
            const parallax = document.querySelector('.hero-section');
            if (parallax) {
                const speed = scrolled * 0.5;
                parallax.style.transform = `translateY(${speed}px)`;
            }
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>